{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I noticed a startup edge case while reviewing the worker path: in local Compose, the worker can come up before `alembic upgrade head` has been run. I\u2019m tightening that now so the long-running worker loop logs schema problems and keeps po...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_53", "text": "I noticed a startup edge case while reviewing the worker path: in local Compose, the worker can come up before `alembic upgrade head` has been run. I\u2019m tightening that now so the long-running worker loop logs schema problems and keeps polling instead of crash-looping on an unmigrated database.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 104, "prompt_index": 19, "prompt_name": "18 \u2014 Postgres-Backed Job Runner Skeleton", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T00:46:50-07:00"}
