{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The live Compose smoke test surfaced a real repo-specific blocker: the local `secrets.yaml` on this machine contains extra provider keys that the backend settings model rejects, so the worker crash-looped before it ever reached Postgres....", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_81", "text": "The live Compose smoke test surfaced a real repo-specific blocker: the local `secrets.yaml` on this machine contains extra provider keys that the backend settings model rejects, so the worker crash-looped before it ever reached Postgres. I\u2019m isolating the worker from that file in Compose with explicit env defaults so the new service can start independently and still be overrideable later.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 155, "prompt_index": 19, "prompt_name": "18 \u2014 Postgres-Backed Job Runner Skeleton", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T00:50:53-07:00"}
