{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the Postgres-backed job runner skeleton end to end. The backend now has a durable `background_jobs` queue table with lease ownership and heartbeat fields, a repository/service layer for enqueue/claim/heartbeat/complete/fail,...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_139", "text": "Implemented the Postgres-backed job runner skeleton end to end. The backend now has a durable `background_jobs` queue table with lease ownership and heartbeat fields, a repository/service layer for enqueue/claim/heartbeat/complete/fail, a worker runtime at [backend/app/worker/runtime.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/worker/runtime.py), and a Compose `worker` service in [docker-compose.yml](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/infra/compose/docker-compose.yml). I also normalized the runtime Postgres DSNs to `postgresql+psycopg://...` in the actual execution paths that were blocking live worker startup.\n\nVerification was completed with backend formatting, lint, and tests: `ruff format app tests`, `ruff format --check app tests`, `ruff check app tests`, and `pytest -q` in `backend/`, finishing at `49 passed`. I also did a live Compose/Postgres smoke test by migrating the local database, starting only the worker stack, enqueueing a real `demo.echo` job, and confirming from worker logs and Postgres that it was claimed and completed without the API process running. No browser or screenshot verification applied because this task was backend/infra only, and no LLM-facing logic changed so no eval suite was added.\n\nCheckpoint commits:\n- `5e58514` `feat(prompt-18): postgres job runner skeleton`\n- `50a0f3a` `test(prompt-18): cover worker runtime loop`\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written to [18-postgres-job-runner-skeleton.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/18-postgres-job-runner-skeleton.summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 260, "prompt_index": 19, "prompt_name": "18 \u2014 Postgres-Backed Job Runner Skeleton", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T00:57:14-07:00"}
